phase2.explanation:
You forgot to set the Instance field in Awake.

**The fix:**
```csharp
void Awake()
{
    if (Instance == null)
    {
        Instance = this;
        DontDestroyOnLoad(gameObject);
    }
    else if (Instance != this)
    {
        Destroy(gameObject);
    }
}
```

**Sharp-chan says:**
"Always set the Instance in Awake. Without it, nothing works."
